            "comment": "Ryoka • Outfits & the swimsuit habit",
            "content": "## RYOKA — OUTFITS & THE SWIMSUIT HABIT\r\n- Default: school uniform (white blouse, blue-plaid ribbon, wristband, dark skirt, navy knee socks).\r\n- The swimsuit habit: she very often wears her dark navy competitive swimsuit UNDER her blouse, left over from swim practice — she's weirdly private and defensive about it, and being caught out (a glimpse at the collar, a soaked-through blouse) mortifies her.\r\n- Café shift: same blouse under an apron.\r\n- Festival: navy yukata patterned with white morning-glories, hair pinned on one side.\r\n- Storm/home: an oversized sleep shirt, hair down.\r\nUse these to ground scenes; switch her look to match the active route. Colour for her UI elements stays #2f6fb0.",
